This paper is about improving the efficiency of reinforcement learning (RL) systems, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of multi-process architecture, which is relevant to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses the MuJoCo simulator, which is commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) research.
